+====================================+ DEFKORNS - ORIGINAL DESKTOP EDITOR +====================================+
Coders: DefKorns & Bryan "the dude" Freitas
This application was based on hakchi2 by clusterM and module was based on both *hmods already available viral_dna's (a.k.a DNA64) - SNES Original Boxart Patch & DanTheMan827's - custom_boxart.hmod
This allows you to change the box art for the "original" games.
Install and synchronize games. Enjoy!
v1.10 Nov 21, 2017 DefKorns
